  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Cost: 4-8 Creation Points </p><p></p><p>You throw your B.I.M and it explodes with spikes that cover the ground.</p><p> The ground is covered in a 20-foot radius of spikes on a point within range.</p><p> The area becomes difficult terrain for the duration.</p><p> When a creature moves into or within the area, it takes 2d4 piercing damage for every 5 feet it travels.</p><p> Upgraded: For every 2 Creation Points after the minimum initial cost increase the damage dice by 1 and increase the radius by 5 feet.</p><p></p>",
